WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.835
Ladies and gentlemen, you're all invited
to attend the wedding of my daughter.

00:00:04.905 --> 00:00:08.306
The wedding will take place
exactly as planned.

00:00:08.375 --> 00:00:11.139
That is, with the exception
of a slight change.

00:00:11.212 --> 00:00:14.841
She will be married
to Mr. Robert Adams.

00:00:14.915 --> 00:00:17.349
Hooray! Hooray!

00:00:17.418 --> 00:00:20.546
Hooray! Hooray! Hooray!

00:00:20.621 --> 00:00:22.714
The skies

00:00:22.790 --> 00:00:27.352
Will all be blue

00:00:27.428 --> 00:00:29.953
When my dreams

00:00:30.030 --> 00:00:34.797
Come true
